<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />You have made the land tremble; you have torn it apart;</para>

<para style="q1">heal its fissures, for it is shaking.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />You have made your people see difficult things;</para>

<para style="q1">you have made us drink the wine of staggering.</para>
